title: Telli Swift & Sliding Into DMs
description:
Lala re-popped her DM cherry, is working on her game, and celebrating the moment! Former WAGS Atlanta star, Telli Swift, also joins to talk motherhood, career goals, the good and bad of reality TV, and life with fiancée Deontay Wilder and their 8 kids! Telli shares their love story from first meeting at LAX to the moment she knew he was the one, and reveals her hopes for their future. Plus, Lala answers your voicemails about a possible second book, the Give Them Lala Beauty line, and whether psychic medium Chris Medina actually predicted the break-up of her relationship when he guested on the podcast last Fall.
